{"tid":1900732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國宣佈瘟疫開始 社區爆發傳染鏈無法再查","createTime":"2020-02-27T11:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T17:00:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9da0a9d43a23e50aa7a50a91068a9c43e477a9f6","tid":1900732,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"德國宣佈瘟疫開始 社區爆發傳染鏈無法再查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2575886/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E7%98%9F%E7%96%AB%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%20%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E9%8F%88%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%86%8D%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2575886%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E7%2598%259F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B%2520%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259F%2593%25E9%258F%2588%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259F%25A5&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=837349d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2575886/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E7%98%9F%E7%96%AB%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%20%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E9%8F%88%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%86%8D%E6%9F%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情在歐洲多國擴散，英法德三國都有雙位數確診。德國更坦言，新冠肺炎已在德國本地開始成為瘟疫（epidemic），因為病人傳染途徑已無法再追查，相信是社區爆發。<br />\n<br />\n德國周三（26日）證實新增5宗新冠肺炎確診病例，使總數增至18宗。病人都來自德國西部北威州，以及南部巴符州。<br />\n<br />\n德國衛生部長施潘（Jens Spahn）表示，新增5宗個案意味德國疫情進入新階段，接觸過病人的人數量很多，情況與此前10多宗個案，都能追蹤傳染鏈到中國源頭不同。<br />\n<br />\n但施潘呼籲，公眾應避免不必要恐慌。他強調德國醫院隔離設施充足，能應付更大數量確診病人，而「不是所有咳嗽都是新冠肺炎」。<br />\n<br />\n意大利是歐洲新冠肺炎疫情前線。歐洲疾控中心數字顯示，截至周三，意大利共有322宗確診個案；德國、法國及英國分別以18時14及13宗隨後。奧地利、俄羅斯、比利時、克羅地亞、芬蘭、瑞典、瑞士都各自有1至2宗個案。"},{"pid":"048a7c460208189a9f44a6c98ff234748a6b0497","tid":1900732,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d634acb6960bc90c423c238a008c93b3dc0e342","tid":1900732,"uid":288707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"肥婆開心晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4a5fc4c9aee1ed4b31ccb0fa074c547ee0ef37","tid":1900732,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"學中國封城囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721e3ca640b5895cc251b58b7a4f19d5973f808d","tid":1900732,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"Failed state"},{"pid":"6d7fd93486eefd968537471498816243d6c5dc8b","tid":1900732,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"懲罰白皮豬助養支那到咁肥壯既報應黎"},{"pid":"e353f0b88e4184da53bf1a2f6f5fa34db8f94edb","tid":1900732,"uid":15815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:02:52.000Z","msg":"One world 🌎 one family <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWelcome 19 virus 🦠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6bb2448f971ffcf1ca4dfcbc91094e68176542","tid":1900732,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68769fd0b59db97075eecde5396c0bdbe972b9b7","tid":1900732,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"18宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e616c36610711445381a862ede3f273dc8ee852","tid":1900732,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci